{"tid":1897764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"問題係個制度！","createTime":"2020-02-26T02:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T04:28:32.000Z","uid":5843,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6f29a40925478bc4a8cd225ed466653d1bb8f982","tid":1897764,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:12:29.000Z","msg":"沈路線：爭立法會-&gt;1200人選委入面爭最多席-&gt;選民主派特首-&gt; a. 任命-&gt;特首用佢嘅權力改革立法會 / b.-&gt;支共唔肯任命-&gt;世界可以制裁支共違憲-&gt;真獨立<br />\n<br />\n無可否認，呢個諗法係好理想，輸咗咪繼續街頭抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面當獨/本土派人參選，傳統泛民有機會到時又捉鬼，大家要清楚呢樣野，贏咗咪拎資源幫手足。<br />\n<br />\n區選選嚟冇用，立法會選嚟冇用，特首1200人選舉都係冇用。但美國就咁插手嘅機會都好低，我地等美國幫手嘅時候咪繼續盡做囉，愈近立法會分裂愈勁。泛民vs本土vs 支共，大家記住你想嘅香港變成點，就點投。<br />\n<br />\n記住唯一出路<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"da6cf1cb36088b6a2c249efcc8f04d5f1bd1e844","tid":1897764,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:26:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc921a35588f7b3333737e0d823e9eee47ffa942","tid":1897764,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:33:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b34e8888effcaaf286907b706f1b5a1d58bb33fd","tid":1897764,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048b8272c5ae83bb8f1ec079fd887275fdac0931","tid":1897764,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc921a35588f7b3333737e0d823e9eee47ffa942","tid":1897764,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:33:38.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"正經Po冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b436525a2c350a89c791ca460a2cd088b386e1","tid":1897764,"uid